**TechNova Solutions – Leave Policy**

**1. Annual Leave**
Employees are entitled to 20 days of paid annual leave per year. Unused leaves cannot be carried forward to the next year.

**2. Sick Leave**
Employees can take up to 10 days of sick leave per year. Medical proof may be required for leaves longer than 2 consecutive days.

**3. Casual Leave**
Employees are allowed 5 days of casual leave annually for personal reasons.

**4. Leave Approval Process**
All leave requests must be applied through the internal portal and approved by the reporting manager in advance.

**5. Unapproved Leave**
Any leave taken without prior approval will be considered unpaid leave and may lead to salary deduction.

**6. Emergency Leave**
In case of emergencies, employees must inform their manager as soon as possible.

